1
00:00:14,180 --> 00:00:15,348
Mulai sekarang,

2
00:00:16,599 --> 00:00:18,226
boleh saya ikut kata hati?

3
00:00:27,527 --> 00:00:29,821
Saya…

4
00:00:29,904 --> 00:00:32,657
Kamu buat apa di situ?
Masuklah, Kyeong-nam!

5
00:00:35,702 --> 00:00:36,786
Marilah masuk.

6
00:00:41,624 --> 00:00:43,877
Kenapa awak tak ingat awak lukis apa?

7
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:46,504
Episod 17,
ciuman pertama Si-woo dan Na-ra.

8
00:00:46,588 --> 00:00:49,466
Datin Jang datang tampar dia.
Awak tak ingatkah?

9
00:00:49,549 --> 00:00:52,302
Kenapa awak hafal komik saya? Peliklah.

10
00:00:52,385 --> 00:00:54,471
Saya baca sebab benci.

11
00:00:54,554 --> 00:00:58,099
Awak hina kerja saya?
Awak melukis pun tak pandai.

12
00:00:58,183 --> 00:01:01,394
Penulis komik bukan sekadar
kena pandai melukis.

13
00:01:01,478 --> 00:01:04,773
Yang penting rajin dan kreatif.
Ingat sikit.

14
00:01:04,856 --> 00:01:08,151
Awak tak layak nak cakap tentang rajin.

15
00:01:08,234 --> 00:01:11,988
Saya dengar Park dan Seo
terpaksa balik lambat setiap Jumaat.

16
00:01:13,865 --> 00:01:17,702
Awak ada komik Jumaat lainkah?
Sebab saya hantar kerja awal.

17
00:01:18,578 --> 00:01:19,412
Ya…

18
00:01:21,873 --> 00:01:22,957
Sebenarnya…

19
00:01:23,041 --> 00:01:26,836
Mesti dia tak boleh balik awal
sebab dia kena betulkan fail awak.

20
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:27,962
Mana ada.

21
00:01:28,046 --> 00:01:30,507
Standard saya tinggi, jadi…

22
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:32,592
- Apa?
- Sebab itulah.

23
00:01:34,135 --> 00:01:37,138
Mesti awak nak kerja
dengan orang yang pandai lukis.

24
00:01:37,847 --> 00:01:39,808
Tapi Hwany pandai melukis.

25
00:01:40,391 --> 00:01:41,559
Apa? Siapa?

26
00:01:41,643 --> 00:01:45,730
Awak lukis gambar itu, bukan?

27
00:01:47,398 --> 00:01:49,984
Apa? Itu gaya asal lukisan awak?

28
00:01:50,068 --> 00:01:52,195
Bukan saya yang lukis.

29
00:01:52,278 --> 00:01:55,824
Yakah? Patutlah cantik. Siapa lukis?

30
00:01:56,991 --> 00:01:58,618
- Dia.
- Apa?

31
00:02:01,037 --> 00:02:03,331
Dia hadiahkan semasa saya pindah sini.

32
00:02:03,414 --> 00:02:05,291
Macam mana awak pandai melukis?

33
00:02:05,375 --> 00:02:07,043
Kamu tak tahukah?

34
00:02:07,585 --> 00:02:10,672
Dia cikgu tuisyen seni saya
sebelum saya masuk kolej.

35
00:02:10,755 --> 00:02:11,589
Betulkah?

36
00:02:11,673 --> 00:02:15,301
Itu kerja sambilan saya
semasa zaman kolej.

37
00:02:15,969 --> 00:02:19,139
Awak patut jadi pelukis.
Sayanglah, awak ada bakat.

38
00:02:19,222 --> 00:02:20,473
Betul tak?

39
00:02:21,141 --> 00:02:23,560
Nampak? Orang lain pun setuju.

40
00:02:23,643 --> 00:02:26,688
Isy. Ramai orang boleh lukis macam saya.

41
00:02:26,771 --> 00:02:28,606
Eh, taklah.

42
00:02:30,692 --> 00:02:33,611
- Risau tentang diri awak dulu.
- Saya tahulah.

43
00:02:35,363 --> 00:02:37,365
Ini episod seterusnya.

44
00:02:37,907 --> 00:02:38,741
Macam mana?

45
00:02:39,909 --> 00:02:41,536
Awak suka tak?

46
00:02:41,619 --> 00:02:43,079
- Suka.
- Bagus, bukan?

47
00:02:50,503 --> 00:02:52,672
Hwany, boleh saya pinjam pengecas?

48
00:02:52,755 --> 00:02:55,341
Ya, ada satu di sebelah sofa.

49
00:03:14,277 --> 00:03:15,486
<i>Dia tidur?</i>

50
00:03:16,362 --> 00:03:19,532
<i>Mulai sekarang, boleh saya ikut kata hati?</i>

51
00:03:20,033 --> 00:03:22,118
<i>Apa sebenarnya dia nak buat?</i>

52
00:03:34,255 --> 00:03:35,256
Awak okey?

53
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:38,176
Apa? Kenapa tanya?

54
00:03:38,885 --> 00:03:39,719
Itu.

55
00:03:41,346 --> 00:03:42,347
Itu?

56
00:03:58,529 --> 00:03:59,364
Ini.

57
00:04:07,413 --> 00:04:08,831
Dah makin baik.

58
00:04:14,003 --> 00:04:15,171
<i>Habislah aku.</i>

59
00:04:21,719 --> 00:04:23,638
EPISOD 8
PERMAINAN NASIB

60
00:04:34,857 --> 00:04:35,942
Awak okey?

61
00:04:36,025 --> 00:04:37,193
Kacaulah!

62
00:04:40,154 --> 00:04:41,030
Rindulah.

63
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,285
<i>Mulai sekarang,</i>

64
00:04:45,785 --> 00:04:47,662
boleh saya ikut kata hati?

65
00:04:49,914 --> 00:04:51,457
Lari!

66
00:05:05,054 --> 00:05:06,055
Helo?

67
00:05:06,139 --> 00:05:08,391
<i>Awak di mana? Saya dekat rumah awak.</i>

68
00:05:08,474 --> 00:05:09,976
Awak buat apa di sini?

69
00:05:10,643 --> 00:05:12,979
<i>Saya serabut, jadi saya keluar joging.</i>

70
00:05:13,062 --> 00:05:13,980
Tak sejukkah?

71
00:05:14,063 --> 00:05:16,733
Boleh saya datang?
Saya dah beli baulu ikan.

72
00:05:16,816 --> 00:05:19,777
<i>Kenapa lambat cakap?</i>
<i>Saya dah keluar pergi kedai.</i>

73
00:05:19,861 --> 00:05:20,695
Apa?

74
00:05:21,738 --> 00:05:22,780
Beli-belah lagi?

75
00:05:22,864 --> 00:05:26,242
Tak, pembersih vakum saya rosak.
jadi saya kena beli baru.

76
00:05:26,743 --> 00:05:29,037
<i>Hei, itu pun kira beli-belah.</i>

77
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:29,954
Yakah?

78
00:05:30,038 --> 00:05:33,166
Pengantin baru suka kedai kita,
jadi jelaskan tentang…

79
00:05:33,249 --> 00:05:34,500
Alamak!

80
00:05:34,584 --> 00:05:36,044
…diskaun dan promosi.

81
00:05:36,127 --> 00:05:38,004
- Beri layanan peribadi.
<i>- Helo?</i>

82
00:05:38,087 --> 00:05:40,131
<i>- Kenapa?</i>
- Saya terkejut tadi.

83
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:44,594
Saya terlupa mamat yang dating
dengan saya kerja di sini.

84
00:05:45,511 --> 00:05:49,182
<i>Macam mana sekarang?</i>
<i>Saya kena beli pembersih vakum.</i>

85
00:05:49,265 --> 00:05:51,517
Baguslah, awak boleh minta diskaun.

86
00:05:51,601 --> 00:05:54,103
<i>Awak gila?</i>
<i>Lepas dating, saya terus senyap.</i>

87
00:05:54,771 --> 00:05:56,439
Nanti saya telefon baliklah.

88
00:05:57,190 --> 00:06:00,026
Jadi, bersedia.
Barang dengan diskaun besar…

89
00:06:00,109 --> 00:06:02,779
Makin banyaklah tempat
aku tak boleh pergi.

90
00:06:03,696 --> 00:06:05,198
Padan muka aku.

91
00:06:06,949 --> 00:06:09,786
<i>Cinta yang anda impikan</i>
<i>akan direalisasikan.</i>

92
00:06:10,703 --> 00:06:12,914
<i>Terdapat 900 tema khas untuk anda.</i>

93
00:06:13,956 --> 00:06:17,293
<i>Pilihlah, anda akan bercinta</i>
<i>dengan siapa hari ini?</i>

94
00:06:20,129 --> 00:06:21,714
NAEMO

95
00:06:40,608 --> 00:06:41,442
Helo.

96
00:06:42,235 --> 00:06:43,569
- <i>Pintu dibuka.</i>
- Hai.

97
00:06:53,621 --> 00:06:54,831
<i>Pintu ditutup.</i>

98
00:07:16,227 --> 00:07:17,770
Saya nak naik dengan awak.

99
00:07:42,295 --> 00:07:43,629
Hai.

100
00:07:43,713 --> 00:07:44,797
Baru sampai?

101
00:08:05,485 --> 00:08:07,570
Fokuslah buat kerja.

102
00:08:17,788 --> 00:08:18,623
Ada apa?

103
00:08:21,501 --> 00:08:24,086
Awak datang cari saya?

104
00:08:51,239 --> 00:08:52,865
Saya cari ini.

105
00:08:56,035 --> 00:08:57,370
Saya ingat apa tadi.

106
00:08:58,037 --> 00:08:59,539
Ambillah.

107
00:09:00,081 --> 00:09:00,915
Okey.

108
00:09:04,585 --> 00:09:07,088
Nah, minumlah sambil kerja.

109
00:09:08,839 --> 00:09:10,132
Awak beli untuk saya?

110
00:09:10,216 --> 00:09:12,677
Ya. Alang-alang saya datang sini…

111
00:09:15,346 --> 00:09:17,765
Saya baru perasan dah tak ada.

112
00:09:19,433 --> 00:09:20,518
Apa yang tak ada?

113
00:09:21,852 --> 00:09:22,687
Rambut depan.

114
00:09:24,605 --> 00:09:25,606
Gaya itu cantik.

115
00:09:30,069 --> 00:09:30,903
Pergi dulu.

116
00:09:31,779 --> 00:09:32,697
Okey.

117
00:10:03,394 --> 00:10:04,770
<i>Jangan fikir pasal dia.</i>

118
00:10:04,854 --> 00:10:07,148
<i>Jangan tunjuk gelabah!</i>

119
00:10:07,231 --> 00:10:08,608
Bawa bertenang!

120
00:10:25,249 --> 00:10:26,334
Seo Mi-rae.

121
00:10:29,462 --> 00:10:31,714
Nah. Awak punya.

122
00:10:32,965 --> 00:10:33,841
Ini…

123
00:10:33,924 --> 00:10:35,468
Saya terjumpa di lobi.

124
00:10:37,136 --> 00:10:40,056
Saya ingat dah hilang. Terima kasih.

125
00:10:40,973 --> 00:10:41,974
Ini…

126
00:10:42,725 --> 00:10:43,934
hadiah saya.

127
00:10:45,478 --> 00:10:48,648
Saya yang letak
dalam kotak cabutan hadiah.

128
00:10:50,775 --> 00:10:53,527
Awak yang beli? Benda ini?

129
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:57,823
Ya, saya main beli saja
dan letak dalam kotak itu.

130
00:11:00,660 --> 00:11:03,287
- Saya baru tahu.
- Nama pun cabutan misteri.

131
00:11:06,207 --> 00:11:08,125
Terima kasihlah.

132
00:11:08,709 --> 00:11:10,378
Okey. Jumpa esok.

133
00:11:14,924 --> 00:11:15,925
Seo Mi-rae?

134
00:11:17,927 --> 00:11:20,262
Awak nak pasang balik tak?

135
00:11:24,934 --> 00:11:26,102
Tapi ikut awaklah.

136
00:11:46,497 --> 00:11:47,748
Gila aku jadinya.

137
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:53,754
<i>Selamat malam.</i>

138
00:11:55,631 --> 00:11:56,465
Apa hal?

139
00:12:04,974 --> 00:12:06,142
PARK
SELAMAT MALAM

140
00:12:07,643 --> 00:12:10,813
Dia hantar mesej peribadi?

141
00:12:11,397 --> 00:12:12,857
Gila apa?

142
00:12:13,441 --> 00:12:14,275
Selamat malam.

143
00:12:15,484 --> 00:12:18,988
Selamat malam.

144
00:12:22,450 --> 00:12:24,201
Ini memang gila.

145
00:12:32,293 --> 00:12:33,127
Apa?

146
00:12:34,044 --> 00:12:36,046
Kenapa aku nampak penat sangat?

147
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:47,850
Semuanya tak jadi.

148
00:12:48,517 --> 00:12:50,728
<i>Saya baru perasan dah tak ada.</i>

149
00:12:50,811 --> 00:12:51,812
Rambut depan.

150
00:12:53,022 --> 00:12:54,273
Gaya itu cantik.

151
00:13:15,002 --> 00:13:15,836
Tarik…

152
00:13:27,431 --> 00:13:28,557
Apa? Apa hal?

153
00:13:28,641 --> 00:13:32,019
Awak bersolek, tapi kenapa pakai topi?

154
00:13:32,895 --> 00:13:33,729
Apa?

155
00:13:35,648 --> 00:13:37,316
Entah, saja-saja.

156
00:13:40,528 --> 00:13:42,112
Kerja sampai tak tidur?

157
00:13:42,196 --> 00:13:44,615
Supaya <i>DYPD </i>dapat nombor satu semula?

158
00:13:44,698 --> 00:13:46,283
Jangan kerja kuat sangat.

159
00:13:46,367 --> 00:13:49,036
Awak nampak penat sangat.

160
00:13:49,119 --> 00:13:49,954
Betul.

161
00:13:51,372 --> 00:13:52,373
Nampak penat?

162
00:13:52,456 --> 00:13:54,959
- Jom makan sedap-sedap.
- Idea menarik.

163
00:13:55,042 --> 00:13:57,503
Platform dan genrenya kekal sama.

164
00:13:57,586 --> 00:14:00,589
Bagi mereka, permainan
berdasarkan siri baru…

165
00:14:00,673 --> 00:14:02,842
Bukan main lagi Kyeong-nam.

166
00:14:02,925 --> 00:14:07,930
Tak cukup dengan jatuhkan <i>DYPD</i>,
nak buat permainan <i>PlanC </i>pula.

167
00:14:09,974 --> 00:14:12,268
Permainan? Permainan apa?

168
00:14:12,768 --> 00:14:15,938
Dia tengah buat
rundingan serius dengan DU.

169
00:14:16,021 --> 00:14:19,358
Semua projeknya menjadi.
Dia memang ada sentuhan ajaib.

170
00:14:19,441 --> 00:14:22,862
Kalau beginilah gayanya,
memang Hwany pegang takhta komik.

171
00:14:22,945 --> 00:14:25,614
En. Hwang pun senyum sampai ke telinga.

172
00:14:25,698 --> 00:14:28,284
Saya paling takut dengan Kyeong-nam.

173
00:14:28,367 --> 00:14:30,452
Dia bukan biasa-biasa.

174
00:14:35,332 --> 00:14:36,250
Hei.

175
00:14:38,294 --> 00:14:39,128
Helo?

176
00:14:40,838 --> 00:14:42,172
Helo!

177
00:14:42,673 --> 00:14:43,507
Ya?

178
00:14:43,591 --> 00:14:45,259
Awak tak dengar cakap saya.

179
00:14:45,342 --> 00:14:47,511
Kenapa termenung jauh sangat?

180
00:14:48,012 --> 00:14:49,263
Maaf, awak cakap apa?

181
00:14:50,097 --> 00:14:53,350
Saya dah buat X-ray tangan.

182
00:14:53,434 --> 00:14:57,187
Sakitnya teruk sangat,
nak makan pun kena guna tangan kiri.

183
00:14:57,271 --> 00:14:59,273
Macam mana nak pegang penyepit?

184
00:14:59,356 --> 00:15:00,441
Betul.

185
00:15:01,609 --> 00:15:03,819
Jadi, janganlah pesan mi untuk kita.

186
00:15:06,155 --> 00:15:07,656
Okey. Faham.

187
00:15:19,084 --> 00:15:23,213
Tak cukup dengan jatuhkan <i>DYPD</i>,
nak buat permainan <i>PlanC </i>pula.

188
00:15:23,297 --> 00:15:26,717
Kalau beginilah gayanya,
memang Hwany pegang takhta komik.

189
00:15:27,676 --> 00:15:28,677
Cik Yun!

190
00:15:29,553 --> 00:15:32,014
Tahu tak kedudukan kita dalam bahaya?

191
00:15:32,097 --> 00:15:34,224
Kita kena fokus.

192
00:15:34,308 --> 00:15:36,727
<i>PlanC </i>makin jauh ke depan.

193
00:15:36,810 --> 00:15:38,479
Nak bercinta itu tak salah,

194
00:15:38,562 --> 00:15:41,482
tapi takkan awak nak abaikan saja <i>DYPD</i>?

195
00:15:42,483 --> 00:15:44,777
Kenapa serius tiba-tiba?

196
00:15:45,277 --> 00:15:46,820
Salahkah saya mesej pakwe?

197
00:15:46,904 --> 00:15:48,238
Apa faedahnya

198
00:15:48,322 --> 00:15:50,699
kalau ada jantan dalam hidup kita?

199
00:15:51,533 --> 00:15:52,993
- Apa?
- Cuba fikir!

200
00:15:53,077 --> 00:15:55,955
Berbaloikah bercinta
kalau periuk nasi terjejas?

201
00:15:56,038 --> 00:15:58,374
Tak berbaloi, Cik Yun. Tak berbaloi.

202
00:15:59,291 --> 00:16:00,876
Kenapa garang tiba-tiba?

203
00:16:01,961 --> 00:16:05,297
- Pandai-pandailah saya uruskan.
- Tak boleh.

204
00:16:18,268 --> 00:16:19,770
Awak naik tren, bukan?

205
00:16:20,604 --> 00:16:23,565
Saya pun rasa nak naik tren.
Jom jalan sama-sama.

206
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:43,002
Sebenarnya, awak pakai topi
supaya saya rasa awak tak cantikkah?

207
00:16:43,085 --> 00:16:43,919
Apa?

208
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:48,507
Topi ini? Eh, taklah.

209
00:16:49,717 --> 00:16:50,634
Saya teka saja.

210
00:16:54,763 --> 00:16:58,017
Saya baru teringat.
Saya naik bas hari ini.

211
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:59,727
Apa? Naik bas pula?

212
00:16:59,810 --> 00:17:01,562
Ya. Jalan baik-baik.

213
00:17:01,645 --> 00:17:02,479
Tunggu!

214
00:17:16,827 --> 00:17:18,203
Tapi bas itu…

215
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:22,541
Pakai tali keledar.
Kita nak masuk lebuh raya.

216
00:17:23,208 --> 00:17:24,293
Lebuh raya?

217
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:28,672
Tumpang tanya, bas ini nak ke mana?

218
00:17:28,756 --> 00:17:29,590
Incheon.

219
00:17:30,174 --> 00:17:31,592
Incheon?

220
00:17:32,342 --> 00:17:33,218
STESEN INCHEON

221
00:17:33,302 --> 00:17:35,721
Pergilah duduk balik. Bahaya!

222
00:17:37,639 --> 00:17:39,224
<i>Kenapa dia tak beritahu?</i>

223
00:17:49,026 --> 00:17:50,444
Orang yang kenalkan kita

224
00:17:50,527 --> 00:17:54,239
kata ini janji temu terakhir awak,
tak kira apa yang berlaku.

225
00:17:55,532 --> 00:17:56,366
Betul.

226
00:17:56,450 --> 00:17:57,785
Kenapa, ya?

227
00:18:00,454 --> 00:18:02,956
Saya dah penat.

228
00:18:05,375 --> 00:18:06,293
Saya pun.

229
00:18:06,376 --> 00:18:09,546
Susah nak cari orang yang kita suka.

230
00:18:09,630 --> 00:18:10,672
Saya setuju.

231
00:18:10,756 --> 00:18:11,965
Apa yang awak cari?

232
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:15,844
Saya suka…

233
00:18:17,012 --> 00:18:19,264
lelaki yang ada banyak sisi berbeza.

234
00:18:19,348 --> 00:18:22,476
- Banyak sisi berbeza?
- Ya.

235
00:18:23,352 --> 00:18:25,270
Lelaki yang segak tapi seksi,

236
00:18:25,354 --> 00:18:26,522
baik tapi nakal,

237
00:18:26,605 --> 00:18:28,107
pandai tapi kalut sikit.

238
00:18:28,190 --> 00:18:30,859
Dia ada kerja tetap tapi berjiwa bebas,

239
00:18:30,943 --> 00:18:33,779
minat membaca tapi tak nampak skema,

240
00:18:33,862 --> 00:18:36,907
berotot sasa tapi berhati lembut,
dan akhir sekali,

241
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:39,701
enggan mengaku dia jatuh hati,

242
00:18:39,785 --> 00:18:41,912
tapi sayang saya sepenuh hati.

243
00:18:44,706 --> 00:18:46,083
- Okey.
- Nak saya sambung?

244
00:18:47,459 --> 00:18:50,045
Sekejap, saya kena jawab panggilan.

245
00:19:20,367 --> 00:19:21,201
Apa?

246
00:19:21,285 --> 00:19:22,703
Lagu pertama ini untuk…

247
00:19:23,328 --> 00:19:27,499
wanita yang permintaannya melampau,
tapi cukup cantik untuk dimaafkan.

248
00:19:29,001 --> 00:19:30,919
Awak dan dia dah putuskah?

249
00:19:32,963 --> 00:19:35,299
Ya, saya rasa…

250
00:19:35,382 --> 00:19:36,967
Saya nak awak lupakan dia.

251
00:19:43,265 --> 00:19:47,769
<i>Kau gadisku, kau gadisku</i>

252
00:19:48,270 --> 00:19:51,690
<i>Kisah kau dan aku</i>

253
00:19:51,773 --> 00:19:55,611
<i>Disinari sang bulan</i>

254
00:19:56,111 --> 00:20:00,073
<i>Kau takdirku, hangat dalam pelukan</i>

255
00:20:00,657 --> 00:20:04,494
<i>Kau gadisku, yang satu</i>

256
00:20:04,578 --> 00:20:08,415
<i>Lagu ini buatmu</i>

257
00:20:08,498 --> 00:20:12,836
<i>Aku cinta padamu</i>

258
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:16,882
<i>Dengarlah luahan</i>

259
00:20:17,549 --> 00:20:19,760
<i>Hatiku</i>

260
00:20:23,555 --> 00:20:27,559
<i>Tahniah, Lee Ji-yeon,</i>
<i>atas pertemuan dengan calon pertama!</i>

261
00:20:46,286 --> 00:20:47,287
Syok betul.

262
00:20:55,879 --> 00:21:00,425
Tak meriah langsung pokok tahun ini.
Maklumlah, En. Hwang sibuk.

263
00:21:00,926 --> 00:21:05,013
Itulah, dulu dia ajak hias sama-sama,
macam dah tradisi kita.

264
00:21:05,097 --> 00:21:06,265
Sedih jugalah.

265
00:21:07,266 --> 00:21:08,267
Sedih?

266
00:21:10,102 --> 00:21:13,605
Yalah, pokok Krismas
kenalah liplap liplap sikit.

267
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:18,443
Amboi, Seo Mi-rae pun syahdu
bila tiba musim raya.

268
00:21:18,944 --> 00:21:20,612
Kamu semua buat apa esok?

269
00:21:20,696 --> 00:21:23,657
Saya rasa nak tonton drama di rumah.

270
00:21:23,740 --> 00:21:26,827
Saya lepak hotel dengan kawan-kawan. Awak?

271
00:21:26,910 --> 00:21:29,579
- Pergi gereja dengan ibu.
- Duduk rumah lagi seronok.

272
00:21:30,247 --> 00:21:32,332
Nak pergi minum lepas habis kerja?

273
00:21:32,958 --> 00:21:35,460
Tapi bar mungkin sesak sebab esok Krismas.

274
00:21:35,544 --> 00:21:37,212
- Saya tak ikut.
- Kenapa?

275
00:21:37,296 --> 00:21:40,215
Malam Krismas pun,
saya tetap kena siapkan <i>DYPD</i>.

276
00:21:42,551 --> 00:21:44,511
Kita pergi tanpa Mi-rae.

277
00:21:45,053 --> 00:21:45,929
Kyeong-nam.

278
00:21:47,264 --> 00:21:48,765
Awak pun kerja malam ini?

279
00:21:49,474 --> 00:21:50,309
Ya.

280
00:21:51,893 --> 00:21:53,061
Kasihannya kamu.

281
00:21:53,562 --> 00:21:58,191
Beritahu Hwany, jangan pulun sangat.
Muda-muda tak rasalah, tapi dah tua nanti…

282
00:22:02,738 --> 00:22:05,365
Nak pergi ke bar hari itu?

283
00:22:14,541 --> 00:22:18,295
Awak ada komik Jumaat lainkah?
Sebab saya hantar kerja awal.

284
00:22:20,088 --> 00:22:20,922
Sebenarnya…

285
00:22:31,475 --> 00:22:32,809
Park Kyeong-nam.

286
00:22:35,103 --> 00:22:38,774
Hwany pun lambat hantar fail kali ini, ya?

287
00:22:39,358 --> 00:22:40,192
Tak.

288
00:22:41,026 --> 00:22:41,860
Apa?

289
00:22:42,569 --> 00:22:43,570
Dia dah hantar.

290
00:22:47,324 --> 00:22:49,076
Habis, kenapa awak belum…

291
00:22:50,786 --> 00:22:52,329
Saya nak ada di sini.

292
00:23:02,005 --> 00:23:04,591
Oh, begitu. Okey!

293
00:23:18,814 --> 00:23:19,648
YUN SONG

294
00:23:24,361 --> 00:23:25,195
MUAT NAIK SELESAI

295
00:23:35,622 --> 00:23:36,456
Apa?

296
00:23:41,128 --> 00:23:41,962
Apa hal?

297
00:23:43,255 --> 00:23:44,256
Elektrik putus?

298
00:24:29,801 --> 00:24:31,636
Awak kata awak sedih, jadi saya hias.

299
00:24:36,224 --> 00:24:37,559
Sedih jugalah.

300
00:24:38,768 --> 00:24:39,853
Sedih?

301
00:24:39,936 --> 00:24:44,733
Yalah, pokok Krismas
kenalah liplap liplap sikit.

302
00:24:52,282 --> 00:24:53,617
Selamat Hari Krismas.

303
00:25:21,269 --> 00:25:22,103
Seo Mi-rae.

304
00:25:25,357 --> 00:25:26,775
Awak naik bas lagi?

305
00:25:29,444 --> 00:25:30,529
Tak.

306
00:25:40,539 --> 00:25:41,373
Terima kasih.

307
00:25:42,332 --> 00:25:45,585
Saya dah rasa suasana Krismas
disebabkan awak. Seronok.

308
00:25:46,962 --> 00:25:48,421
Saya pun seronok.

309
00:25:55,428 --> 00:25:57,556
Saya dengar tentang permainan <i>PlanC</i>.

310
00:25:57,639 --> 00:25:59,474
Tahniah.

311
00:26:00,058 --> 00:26:01,977
Ini baru fasa bincang-bincang.

312
00:26:04,521 --> 00:26:06,982
Kenapa awak pandai serba-serbi?

313
00:26:08,149 --> 00:26:11,236
Mesti awak tak perlu banyak risau.

314
00:26:11,778 --> 00:26:13,196
Semuanya mudah bagi awak.

315
00:26:14,281 --> 00:26:15,574
Awak rasa begitukah?

316
00:26:16,074 --> 00:26:17,200
Sebenarnya tak pun.

317
00:26:25,333 --> 00:26:26,835
PAMERAN SOLO LEE KYU-TAE

318
00:26:26,918 --> 00:26:28,753
Awak kenal pelukis ini?

319
00:26:30,046 --> 00:26:32,674
Saya beli kalendar ilustrasinya
setiap tahun.

320
00:26:33,341 --> 00:26:37,095
Kalau fikir-fikir, sebenarnya
gaya lukisan dia ala-ala awak.

321
00:26:37,596 --> 00:26:39,848
Dulu saya pun minat dia.

322
00:26:41,474 --> 00:26:42,475
Okey.

323
00:26:43,602 --> 00:26:45,520
Pamerannya tamat tak lama lagi.

324
00:26:46,313 --> 00:26:47,147
Betul.

325
00:26:50,525 --> 00:26:51,443
Nak pergi?

326
00:26:56,531 --> 00:26:58,158
Selamba sangatkah bunyinya?

327
00:26:59,534 --> 00:27:01,453
Fikir dulu, nanti cakaplah.

328
00:27:12,339 --> 00:27:13,506
Awak tak lapar?

329
00:27:15,884 --> 00:27:17,886
Awak belum makan malam.

330
00:27:32,901 --> 00:27:36,988
Kenapa awak berhenti melukis?
Awak berbakat besar.

331
00:27:39,282 --> 00:27:40,617
Saya hilang minat.

332
00:27:41,951 --> 00:27:42,786
Apa?

333
00:27:44,245 --> 00:27:46,665
Dulu melukis segala-galanya bagi saya,

334
00:27:47,165 --> 00:27:49,167
tapi tiba-tiba saya tawar hati.

335
00:27:50,293 --> 00:27:52,087
Saya sayang nak tinggalkannya,

336
00:27:52,587 --> 00:27:55,882
tapi saya tak sabar nak cari
sesuatu yang sama hebat.

337
00:27:56,508 --> 00:27:57,926
Jadi, saya berhenti.

338
00:28:00,595 --> 00:28:02,764
Dah jumpa pengganti yang setanding?

339
00:28:03,348 --> 00:28:04,557
Rupanya, susah juga

340
00:28:05,141 --> 00:28:08,728
nak minat sesuatu terus-menerus
tanpa berubah hati.

341
00:28:14,943 --> 00:28:16,611
- Jumpa lagi.
- Okey.

342
00:28:17,862 --> 00:28:19,114
Tunggu…

343
00:28:33,044 --> 00:28:34,462
Nanti bacalah.

344
00:28:35,755 --> 00:28:36,589
Okey.

345
00:28:37,424 --> 00:28:38,258
Pergi dulu.

346
00:29:07,912 --> 00:29:10,665
<i>Nanti marilah kita keluar makan berdua.</i>

347
00:29:19,591 --> 00:29:22,177
<i>Saya nak cakap yang saya suka awak.</i>

348
00:29:33,146 --> 00:29:34,063
PARK KYEONG-NAM

349
00:29:34,147 --> 00:29:35,273
<i>Dah sampai rumah?</i>

350
00:29:40,320 --> 00:29:41,571
DAH SAMPAI

351
00:29:42,238 --> 00:29:43,072
GU YEONG-IL

352
00:29:43,156 --> 00:29:44,908
<i>Sampai bila saya kena tunggu?</i>

353
00:29:50,663 --> 00:29:52,665
SAYA NAK CAKAP YANG SAYA SUKA AWAK

354
00:29:53,792 --> 00:29:56,628
<i>Macam mana aku boleh jadi begini?</i>

355
00:30:04,010 --> 00:30:04,844
Awak datang.

356
00:30:15,355 --> 00:30:17,273
- Hei…
- Eh, dapat ikan.

357
00:30:25,448 --> 00:30:28,618
Umpan awak cuma mengena
setiap kali saya nak cakap.

358
00:30:29,828 --> 00:30:30,662
Nampaknya.

359
00:30:31,579 --> 00:30:32,413
Pelik betul.

360
00:30:37,961 --> 00:30:38,795
Awak kenapa?

361
00:30:48,596 --> 00:30:50,431
Saya dah luahkan perasaan.

362
00:30:50,515 --> 00:30:53,685
Sekarang, awak nak cakap serius
dengan muka serius.

363
00:30:53,768 --> 00:30:54,727
Saya takut.

364
00:30:58,398 --> 00:30:59,524
Takut saya menolak?

365
00:31:00,984 --> 00:31:02,235
Awak nak menolak?

366
00:31:15,456 --> 00:31:17,542
Satu apa pun tak dapat hari ini.

367
00:31:19,210 --> 00:31:20,044
Jomlah.

368
00:31:38,938 --> 00:31:39,939
Nak saya lukis awak?

369
00:31:53,369 --> 00:31:54,370
Relaks saja.

370
00:31:56,331 --> 00:31:57,165
Okey.

371
00:32:08,217 --> 00:32:09,052
<i>Seo Mi-rae.</i>

372
00:32:13,139 --> 00:32:14,474
<i>Saya suka awak.</i>

373
00:32:17,185 --> 00:32:18,186
<i>Mulai sekarang…</i>

374
00:32:20,355 --> 00:32:22,065
<i>boleh saya ikut kata hati?</i>

375
00:32:33,368 --> 00:32:34,369
Kenapa?

376
00:32:41,042 --> 00:32:41,876
Maaf.

377
00:32:43,252 --> 00:32:44,337
Apa?

378
00:32:44,420 --> 00:32:45,338
Saya…

379
00:32:46,339 --> 00:32:48,007
Saya takkan datang lagi.

380
00:32:51,761 --> 00:32:52,595
Kenapa?

381
00:32:53,304 --> 00:32:55,682
Kalau saya cerita pun, awak tak faham.

382
00:32:56,474 --> 00:33:00,311
Tapi makin kita jumpa,
makin saya jatuh cinta dengan seseorang.

383
00:33:01,688 --> 00:33:02,855
Saya rasa macam

384
00:33:03,898 --> 00:33:06,067
saya mudahkan kerja dia.

385
00:33:08,736 --> 00:33:11,739
Maksudnya, semasa awak bersama saya pun,

386
00:33:12,407 --> 00:33:14,742
awak asyik teringat lelaki lain?

387
00:33:20,748 --> 00:33:21,749
Awak suka dia?

388
00:33:27,922 --> 00:33:29,007
Saya tak tahu.

389
00:33:33,428 --> 00:33:35,680
Kenapa awak tak tahu perasaan sendiri?

390
00:33:35,763 --> 00:33:37,015
Saya pun geram.

391
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:40,810
Awak tahu apa rasanya
bila betul-betul jatuh hati?

392
00:33:40,893 --> 00:33:43,229
Mesti awak tak tahu.

393
00:33:43,312 --> 00:33:44,522
Saya tahu.

394
00:33:46,315 --> 00:33:50,486
Ia bererti kita takkan berubah,
walaupun dia berubah.

395
00:33:52,989 --> 00:33:54,407
<i>Saya tak berubah.</i>

396
00:33:54,907 --> 00:33:56,242
Mi-rae.

397
00:33:56,325 --> 00:33:58,161
Kita semua berubah.

398
00:33:58,745 --> 00:34:00,204
Awak pun dah berubah.

399
00:34:05,501 --> 00:34:08,004
Kata-kata awak tentang lukisan awak…

400
00:34:09,297 --> 00:34:12,133
Kenapa awak risau
ada yang berubah atau tidak?

401
00:34:13,259 --> 00:34:16,262
Penting sangatkah?
Kenapa awak peduli sangat?

402
00:34:17,388 --> 00:34:19,891
Ada sebab lainkah?

403
00:34:22,477 --> 00:34:24,562
Saya memang begitu. Apa boleh buat?

404
00:34:26,898 --> 00:34:28,024
Awak memang begitu?

405
00:34:30,401 --> 00:34:32,403
Saya tak terima alasan itu.

406
00:34:33,696 --> 00:34:34,864
<i>Sebab akulah</i>

407
00:34:36,157 --> 00:34:37,408
<i>yang cipta kau.</i>

408
00:34:39,869 --> 00:34:40,995
Seo Mi-rae.

409
00:34:41,871 --> 00:34:43,831
<i>Mesti kau tahu apa yang aku nak…</i>

410
00:34:43,915 --> 00:34:46,292
Kalau awak dah tak suka saya pun…

411
00:34:46,959 --> 00:34:48,711
<i>…dan apa yang aku takut…</i>

412
00:34:48,795 --> 00:34:50,463
…saya takkan berubah.

413
00:34:51,089 --> 00:34:52,924
<i>…seolah-olah kau tahu hati aku.</i>

414
00:34:53,007 --> 00:34:55,426
Saya memang begitu kalau suka orang.

415
00:34:56,052 --> 00:34:59,347
<i>Tak. Mungkin kau lebih tahu</i>
<i>daripada aku sendiri.</i>

416
00:35:00,181 --> 00:35:03,017
Dia ada beritahu awak
yang dia takkan berubah?

417
00:35:11,192 --> 00:35:12,527
<i>Saya hilang minat.</i>

418
00:35:12,610 --> 00:35:14,237
Rupanya, susah juga

419
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:18,116
nak minat sesuatu terus-menerus
tanpa berubah hati.

420
00:35:28,876 --> 00:35:30,628
Apabila dia berubah hati,

421
00:35:31,671 --> 00:35:33,256
awak tak takut terlukakah?

422
00:35:40,930 --> 00:35:42,098
Tapi saya…

423
00:35:44,433 --> 00:35:46,435
takkan sekali-kali melukai awak.

424
00:35:48,604 --> 00:35:49,438
Jadi,

425
00:35:51,315 --> 00:35:52,400
janganlah pergi.

426
00:36:14,005 --> 00:36:15,089
Seo Mi-rae.

427
00:36:22,013 --> 00:36:24,223
- Sesi penilaian akhir.
- Ya.

428
00:36:24,307 --> 00:36:27,185
Genre fantasi sengit tahun ini.
Genre kamu pula?

429
00:36:27,268 --> 00:36:29,478
Samalah dengan kami punya.

430
00:36:29,562 --> 00:36:32,899
Kyeong-nam dan Mi-rae
asyik bergaduh tentang siapa betul.

431
00:36:32,982 --> 00:36:33,816
Okey.

432
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:36,861
En. Hwang tak dapat datang,
jadi mari kita mulakan.

433
00:36:36,944 --> 00:36:37,778
- Okey.
- Jom.

434
00:36:42,408 --> 00:36:46,245
Susunan komik ini dah cantik,
tapi macam ketinggalan zaman.

435
00:36:46,329 --> 00:36:49,874
Betul, tapi sekurang-kurangnya,
ia pilihan selamat.

436
00:36:51,417 --> 00:36:57,256
Boleh tahan, tapi tak cukup hebat.
Lancar tapi kurang menyengat.

437
00:36:59,217 --> 00:37:00,801
Ketepikan dulu?

438
00:37:02,053 --> 00:37:02,970
Okey.

439
00:37:03,054 --> 00:37:04,931
Siapa nak ke tandas?

440
00:37:05,014 --> 00:37:06,724
- Saya.
- Saya pun.

441
00:37:22,073 --> 00:37:24,825
Saya rasa setiap komik perlu ada umph.

442
00:37:24,909 --> 00:37:26,160
Dari segi rujukan…

443
00:37:26,244 --> 00:37:28,496
Alamak, saya tertinggal telefon.

444
00:37:28,579 --> 00:37:29,664
Buatkan kopi.

445
00:37:34,168 --> 00:37:36,003
Silakan, saya tak nak guna.

446
00:37:36,087 --> 00:37:37,088
Seo Mi-rae.

447
00:37:40,466 --> 00:37:41,384
Awak sakit?

448
00:37:44,470 --> 00:37:45,513
Tak.

449
00:37:47,056 --> 00:37:49,058
Awak nampak pucat sikit.

450
00:37:53,729 --> 00:37:55,064
Sebenarnya…

451
00:37:58,109 --> 00:38:03,072
Saya dah faham maksud awak
apabila awak kata

452
00:38:03,572 --> 00:38:05,950
awak nak ikut kata hati.

453
00:38:06,867 --> 00:38:09,120
Tapi apa-apa pun,

454
00:38:09,954 --> 00:38:13,040
kalau boleh, jangan buat di tempat kerja.

455
00:38:16,585 --> 00:38:18,504
Di tempat kerja?

456
00:38:23,009 --> 00:38:24,510
Saya silap cakap.

457
00:38:26,053 --> 00:38:29,390
Jangan buat langsung di mana-mana pun.

458
00:38:31,517 --> 00:38:32,935
Tolonglah.

459
00:38:40,234 --> 00:38:43,070
Apa? Saya kata saya nak kopi.

460
00:38:46,866 --> 00:38:47,867
Awak nak juga?

461
00:38:57,251 --> 00:38:58,919
- Komik seterusnya?
- Okey.

462
00:38:59,503 --> 00:39:02,048
A-606. <i>Elena Mata Delima</i>.

463
00:39:02,631 --> 00:39:06,218
Wah, ini komik apa?
Saya suka gayanya. Siapa yang pilih?

464
00:39:08,304 --> 00:39:11,724
Kami sebenarnya berbeza pendapat
tentang komik ini.

465
00:39:12,308 --> 00:39:13,142
Jadi…

466
00:39:18,397 --> 00:39:19,815
Saya yang pilih.

467
00:39:20,316 --> 00:39:25,571
Kyeong-nam dan Mi-rae
tak sependapat langsung.

468
00:39:28,741 --> 00:39:31,994
Saya rasa komik ini layak.

469
00:39:32,661 --> 00:39:34,663
Mi-rae? Awak masih tak setuju?

470
00:39:36,874 --> 00:39:37,708
Betul.

471
00:39:38,626 --> 00:39:39,460
Saya tak suka.

472
00:39:41,587 --> 00:39:43,464
Karyanya masih nampak amatur.

473
00:39:44,673 --> 00:39:46,592
- Apa yang awak tak suka?
- Apa?

474
00:39:50,763 --> 00:39:53,015
Saya dah beritahu awak banyak kali.

475
00:39:53,099 --> 00:39:55,351
Ini pertandingan untuk penulis baru.

476
00:39:55,434 --> 00:39:59,855
Pengarah suruh fokus pada potensinya.
Saya nampak potensinya.

477
00:40:01,190 --> 00:40:02,775
Saya tak nampak pun.

478
00:40:02,858 --> 00:40:04,860
Awak pernah nak ubah fikiran.

479
00:40:09,073 --> 00:40:10,825
Dari dulu sampai sekarang…

480
00:40:12,284 --> 00:40:13,619
awak memang bencikah?

481
00:40:17,081 --> 00:40:17,915
Ya.

482
00:40:21,252 --> 00:40:22,920
Saya rasa…

483
00:40:25,798 --> 00:40:27,216
itu takkan berubah.

484
00:40:35,641 --> 00:40:37,893
Ya! Mesyuarat macam inilah menarik!

485
00:40:38,394 --> 00:40:42,314
Apa kata kita berhenti dulu
dan sambung bincang esok?

486
00:40:42,398 --> 00:40:44,525
- Okey.
- Terima kasih, semua.

487
00:40:44,608 --> 00:40:46,068
Kita terlebih rajin.

488
00:40:46,569 --> 00:40:47,695
- Syabas.
- Penat.

489
00:40:47,778 --> 00:40:48,779
Jomlah balik.

490
00:40:51,365 --> 00:40:53,367
Terima kasih, semua.

491
00:41:42,416 --> 00:41:44,168
<i>Saya baru teringat</i>

492
00:41:45,169 --> 00:41:49,048
kenapa saya mati-mati
tak nak bercinta lagi.

493
00:41:50,424 --> 00:41:51,592
Tapi

494
00:41:52,218 --> 00:41:56,555
saya betul-betul takut
Kyeong-nam akan berubah…

495
00:42:03,562 --> 00:42:07,441
jadi saya rasa dialah
yang saya betul-betul suka.

496
00:42:09,693 --> 00:42:14,406
Dulu saya ingat awaklah punca
Kyeong-nam buat saya berdebar-debar,

497
00:42:15,449 --> 00:42:17,034
tapi saya rasa sebenarnya…

498
00:42:20,412 --> 00:42:21,747
saya suka dia.

499
00:42:24,208 --> 00:42:25,876
Sebab itu saya tak lepaskan awak.

500
00:42:28,671 --> 00:42:30,214
Saya tak nak awak merana.

501
00:42:31,507 --> 00:42:33,175
Hubungan kamu pasti berakhir

502
00:42:34,593 --> 00:42:36,595
dan awak perlu hadapinya sendiri.

503
00:42:37,096 --> 00:42:38,931
Padahal awak paling benci

504
00:42:40,224 --> 00:42:41,642
kalau putus cinta lagi.

505
00:42:43,227 --> 00:42:44,812
<i>Aku nak lupakannya.</i>

506
00:42:44,895 --> 00:42:46,272
Awak okey?

507
00:42:52,152 --> 00:42:55,406
Alahai, kasihannya awak.

508
00:42:59,159 --> 00:43:02,538
MI-RAE, SE-JUNE

509
00:43:39,033 --> 00:43:40,868
Nah, bebola udang.

510
00:43:42,411 --> 00:43:44,663
- Awak curi saya punya?
- Memanglah.

511
00:43:44,747 --> 00:43:46,957
- Awak memang terbaik.
- Terima kasih.

512
00:43:47,750 --> 00:43:49,084
- Urut sini.
- Okey.

513
00:43:49,168 --> 00:43:50,836
Tegangnya otot kaki awak.

514
00:43:50,919 --> 00:43:52,421
Rambut awak rosak teruk.

515
00:43:52,504 --> 00:43:54,006
Jauhkan pengering sikit.

516
00:43:54,089 --> 00:43:55,174
Okey, maaf.

517
00:43:55,257 --> 00:43:56,091
Tengok.

518
00:43:57,134 --> 00:43:58,636
Kelakar betul. Tengoklah.

519
00:44:02,473 --> 00:44:05,893
<i>Selalunya berdua,</i>
<i>tiba-tiba tinggal seorang.</i>

520
00:44:07,394 --> 00:44:10,648
<i>Apabila saya sedar</i>
<i>yang dia takkan kembali,</i>

521
00:44:11,565 --> 00:44:13,317
<i>sakitnya bukan main terasa.</i>

522
00:44:18,572 --> 00:44:19,907
Awak takut

523
00:44:20,532 --> 00:44:22,201
ia berlaku lagi.

524
00:44:27,498 --> 00:44:29,249
<i>Lelaki yang aku cipta…</i>

525
00:44:31,335 --> 00:44:34,505
<i>meruntuhkan pendirianku</i>
<i>buat kesekian kalinya.</i>

526
00:44:38,759 --> 00:44:39,843
Kau betul.

527
00:44:40,969 --> 00:44:42,137
<i>Tindakan kau betul.</i>

528
00:45:00,280 --> 00:45:02,783
<i>Saya beli kalendar ilustrasinya</i>
<i>setiap tahun.</i>

529
00:45:03,784 --> 00:45:05,035
Nak pergi?

530
00:45:30,853 --> 00:45:35,023
<i>Kalau ia berakhir suatu hari nanti,</i>
<i>lebih baik jangan mulakan.</i>

531
00:45:49,788 --> 00:45:52,291
Penamat episod ini dah cantik.

532
00:45:52,374 --> 00:45:54,293
Tapi bila nak rungkai petunjuk?

533
00:45:57,421 --> 00:45:59,089
Saya nak jawab telefon.

534
00:46:00,340 --> 00:46:01,175
Hai, ibu.

535
00:46:12,686 --> 00:46:15,355
<i>Maaf, tapi nampaknya…</i>

536
00:46:15,439 --> 00:46:19,109
Tiga kopi, tiga kuih.
Apa yang awak cuba sampaikan?

537
00:46:19,610 --> 00:46:21,695
Yalah, sebab kita bertiga…

538
00:46:21,779 --> 00:46:23,864
Balik-balik sebut tiga!

539
00:46:23,947 --> 00:46:26,575
Awak nak sumpah <i>DYPD</i>
jatuh ke tangga ketiga?

540
00:46:26,658 --> 00:46:28,285
<i>…aku tak cukup berani.</i>

541
00:46:57,981 --> 00:47:00,567
LEE KYU-TAE
PAMERAN SOLO

542
00:47:05,322 --> 00:47:07,658
Kamu semua bekerja keras tahun lalu.

543
00:47:07,741 --> 00:47:10,160
- Semoga terus cemerlang!
- Syabas, semua!

544
00:47:10,828 --> 00:47:13,163
Saya nak kongsi berita baik.

545
00:47:13,247 --> 00:47:16,875
Bagi kamu semua, ini mungkin berita sedih.

546
00:47:16,959 --> 00:47:19,253
Mulai tahun ini,

547
00:47:19,336 --> 00:47:23,215
kita akan serius berkecimpung
dalam platform komik web Amerika.

548
00:47:23,298 --> 00:47:26,969
Sebab itu Korea akan hantar
wakil terbaik ke sana.

549
00:47:27,886 --> 00:47:28,720
Siapa?

550
00:47:33,517 --> 00:47:34,351
Sayalah.

551
00:47:37,813 --> 00:47:40,065
Saya akan jadi CEO di Amerika.

552
00:47:41,358 --> 00:47:43,944
Pengarah Hwang! Bukan, CEO Hwang!

553
00:47:44,027 --> 00:47:45,362
- Tolonglah.
- Tahniah!

554
00:47:45,445 --> 00:47:49,992
Tapi tunggang-langganglah kami
kalau bos tinggalkan kami terus!

555
00:47:50,075 --> 00:47:53,871
Hei, saya pergi beberapa bulan lagilah.
Janganlah menangis.

556
00:47:53,954 --> 00:47:58,083
Saya pun berat nak tinggalkan kamu semua.

557
00:47:58,166 --> 00:48:00,419
Mari kita rancang majlis perpisahan.

558
00:48:00,502 --> 00:48:03,839
Ya, sambutan besar-besaran,
khas untuk bos kita.

559
00:48:03,922 --> 00:48:04,756
Betul.

560
00:48:04,840 --> 00:48:07,259
Hei! Saya belanja!

561
00:48:07,342 --> 00:48:08,927
- Hore!
- Saya dah janji.

562
00:48:09,011 --> 00:48:10,429
- Bos baik!
- Terima kasih.

563
00:48:10,512 --> 00:48:12,264
Saya nak habiskan sebelum pergi!

564
00:48:12,347 --> 00:48:14,099
- Jom sambung minum.
- Bos!

565
00:48:15,475 --> 00:48:16,643
- Pergi mana?
- Jom!

566
00:48:16,727 --> 00:48:19,897
- Seronoknya!
- Dia nak ke mana? Hei!

567
00:48:20,814 --> 00:48:21,648
TIADA TEKSI

568
00:48:21,732 --> 00:48:22,733
Sejuknya.

569
00:48:22,816 --> 00:48:24,026
Seo Mi-rae!

570
00:48:25,027 --> 00:48:26,361
Jom naik sama-sama.

571
00:48:26,445 --> 00:48:27,362
Okey.

572
00:48:30,449 --> 00:48:31,617
Terima kasih.

573
00:48:44,171 --> 00:48:47,174
Saya turun dulu, kemudian awak,
barulah Kyeong-nam.

574
00:48:56,391 --> 00:48:57,726
Selamat berehat.

575
00:48:57,809 --> 00:48:59,686
- Terima kasih.
- Selamat malam.

576
00:49:06,318 --> 00:49:07,319
<i>Berita cuaca.</i>

577
00:49:07,402 --> 00:49:11,615
<i>Salji di wilayah tengah</i>
<i>masih berterusan sejak petang tadi</i>

578
00:49:11,698 --> 00:49:14,826
<i>pada kadar kira-kira</i>
<i>satu sentimeter sejam di Seoul,</i>

579
00:49:14,910 --> 00:49:17,871
<i>Gyeonggi-do Utara,</i>
<i>dan Yeongseo, Gangwon-do.</i>

580
00:49:17,955 --> 00:49:19,665
<i>Di seluruh bandar raya…</i>

581
00:49:19,748 --> 00:49:21,750
Encik, saya nak turun di sini.

582
00:49:21,833 --> 00:49:22,668
Okey.

583
00:49:29,341 --> 00:49:32,344
Saya pergi dulu. Selamat bercuti.

584
00:49:32,427 --> 00:49:33,512
Tunggu.

585
00:49:37,140 --> 00:49:38,809
Nah. Salji lebat sangat.

586
00:49:40,268 --> 00:49:42,688
Tak apa, rumah saya di situ saja.

587
00:49:42,771 --> 00:49:44,606
Pergi dulu.

588
00:50:02,499 --> 00:50:03,583
Seo Mi-rae!

589
00:50:13,010 --> 00:50:14,219
Ambillah.

590
00:50:17,597 --> 00:50:18,432
Tapi saya…

591
00:50:19,599 --> 00:50:20,517
Saya okey.

592
00:50:23,145 --> 00:50:24,938
Payung pun awak tak nak ambil?

593
00:50:27,274 --> 00:50:28,108
Apa?

594
00:50:35,073 --> 00:50:36,324
Gunalah.

595
00:50:44,750 --> 00:50:48,462
Macam mana awak nak balik?
Teksi dah tak ada.

596
00:50:51,048 --> 00:50:52,299
Nanti saya fikirlah.

597
00:50:53,133 --> 00:50:53,967
Tunggu.

598
00:50:54,801 --> 00:50:55,761
Park Kyeong-nam.

599
00:50:56,511 --> 00:51:00,474
Ambil balik payung awak. Saya tak nak.

600
00:51:03,560 --> 00:51:05,604
Saya cuma tak nak awak kena salji.

601
00:51:06,813 --> 00:51:08,857
Saya tolong sikit pun tak boleh?

602
00:51:12,569 --> 00:51:13,737
Pernahkah saya

603
00:51:14,446 --> 00:51:16,114
minta awak suka saya?

604
00:51:21,411 --> 00:51:22,412
Awak tak rasa…

605
00:51:24,039 --> 00:51:25,749
awak pentingkan diri?

606
00:51:28,460 --> 00:51:30,670
Awak peduli perasaan awak sajakah?

607
00:51:33,256 --> 00:51:35,258
Pernahkah awak fikir

608
00:51:36,510 --> 00:51:38,011
macam mana saya rasa?

609
00:51:41,056 --> 00:51:42,057
Ini pun

610
00:51:43,058 --> 00:51:44,226
sukar bagi saya.

611
00:51:45,644 --> 00:51:49,648
Saya tak suka rasa berdebar
setiap kali awak usik jiwa saya.

612
00:51:50,273 --> 00:51:51,691
Ini pun susah bagi saya.

613
00:51:53,819 --> 00:51:56,154
Tapi kalau saya berdebar pun kenapa?

614
00:51:57,697 --> 00:51:59,116
Apa yang awak nak?

615
00:52:00,992 --> 00:52:02,494
Nak kita terus bercinta?

616
00:52:05,413 --> 00:52:06,706
Tak bolehkah?

617
00:52:10,168 --> 00:52:11,545
Biar betul awak serius.

618
00:52:11,628 --> 00:52:13,630
Apa yang awak takut sangat?

619
00:52:15,048 --> 00:52:17,134
Kita belum mula lagi pun.

620
00:52:17,217 --> 00:52:18,885
Setiap yang bermula…

621
00:52:21,012 --> 00:52:22,639
pasti berakhir.

622
00:52:22,722 --> 00:52:23,890
Saya…

623
00:52:26,226 --> 00:52:28,145
tak pernah fikir sampai ke situ.

624
00:52:31,064 --> 00:52:34,568
Sekarang memanglah,
tapi lambat-laun awak akan berubah.

625
00:52:34,651 --> 00:52:36,486
Awak bencikah kalau ada yang berubah?

626
00:52:37,612 --> 00:52:40,448
Teruk sangatkah kalau berubah?

627
00:52:43,326 --> 00:52:44,411
Sejak…

628
00:52:47,247 --> 00:52:48,915
jatuh cinta dengan awak…

629
00:52:51,293 --> 00:52:52,460
saya dah berubah.

630
00:57:40,957 --> 00:57:42,667
Terjemahan sari kata oleh FZA

